This one is very meta and very important as this is the plugin information for Neorg, the writing tool that i am using to do this whole config so handling this work is important for making the whole thing run smoothly.

we tried to break this up into various pieces so now we are going to go over them all at once since we primarily get this done within the lazy config so that everything goes well they did a good job of getting everything worked out

